{
  "description": "CRITICAL: Some comments actively harm readability. Delete commented-out code (it's in git), remove misleading or outdated comments, and eliminate redundant noise.",
  "scanner": "agile_bot.bots.base_bot.src.scanners.bad_comments_scanner.BadCommentsScanner",
  "examples": [
    {
      "do": {
        "description": "Remove harmful comments",
        "content": [
          "Delete commented-out code (it's in git)",
          "Remove misleading or outdated comments",
          "Eliminate redundant noise",
          "Keep codebase clean and current",
          "",
          "Correct Examples (clean code):",
          "BEFORE:",
          "// Old implementation",
          "// function processOrder(order) {",
          "//   return order.total * 0.9;",
          "// }",
          "",
          "function processOrder(order) {",
          "  return calculateOrderTotal(order);",
          "}",
          "",
          "AFTER:",
          "function processOrder(order) {",
          "  return calculateOrderTotal(order);",
          "}",
          "(deleted commented code - it's in git history)",
          "",
          "Comment Cleanup Requirements:",
          "- No commented-out code blocks",
          "- No outdated/misleading comments",
          "- No HTML markup in comments",
          "- Comments match current code"
        ]
      },
      "dont": {
        "description": "Don't keep commented-out backup code or misleading comments",
        "content": [
          "Don't keep commented-out 'backup' code",
          "Don't write misleading or contradictory comments",
          "Don't use HTML markup in comments",
          "",
          "Wrong Examples (harmful comments):",
          "// TODO: This needs to be implemented",
          "function processOrder(order) {",
          "  // ... full implementation exists ...",
          "}",
          "(misleading - it IS implemented)",
          "",
          "// Returns user by ID",
          "function getUserByName(name) {...}",
          "(contradictory - comment wrong)",
          "",
          "/**",
          " * <p>Calculates total</p>",
          " * <ul><li>Item 1</li></ul>",
          " */",
          "(HTML in comments)",
          "",
          "Harmful Comment Indicators (DELETE):",
          "- Commented-out code blocks (// old code...)",
          "- Outdated comments not matching code",
          "- Misleading comments contradicting code",
          "- HTML/XML markup in comments",
          "- Commented-out imports/variables",
          "",
          "Action Required:",
          "- Delete ALL commented-out code (use git to retrieve)",
          "- Update or delete outdated comments",
          "- Fix contradictory comments or delete them",
          "- Remove HTML markup from comments"
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}



















































